# Thanks!

Slides son creados via el R package [**xaringan**](https://github.com/yihui/xaringan).

El chacra proviene de [remark.js](https://remarkjs.com), [**knitr**](https://yihui.org/knitr/), y [R Markdown](https://rmarkdown.rstudio.com).
